paragraph: Frode Lamøy (born 2 April 1972) is a Norwegian-born drummer. He has played with bands such as Jack In The Box, Autopulver and TNT. He is also co-founder of the music and website development company Sounds Like You with his brother, Rune Lamøy.
Ronni Le Tekrø - Extra Strong String (2000)
Magne F - Past Perfect Future Tense (2004)
